init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But when he slips back to the day where he first found them, something unexpected happens.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Do you have any idea what time it is?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: And he was closest to his home at the time.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Coming back to his house, Bob was confused as to why he was supposed to come here.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: As he walked through the kitchen, he noticed a strange looking plant.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I don't know why but I think that plant has something to do with me getting back to the present time," Bob thought

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Bob was so curious about the plant that he decided to pick one of the berries and take a bite.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was unable to do anything as he drifted off into an odd dream.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Bob was surprised that he had returned to the present time.
